Here is the translation:

In Gopi's house many are, Gokul doesn't shine; 
Adorned with jewels, Kanak Bhuvan, Many vehicles, chariot in heaven.

Here is the translation:

Lord, sage, Siddh, Gop, Gopi, stay;
His herd stays with Him, milked;

Gopi Radha play together, in harmony go;
Serve Lord Krishna, my love, my master, I'll love.

Here is the translation:

The precious, the inedible, I have done; my precious is very beautiful, it shines; 
White horses, no noise, do not make a sound; good, well-rope, remains, beauty kills.

Here is the translation:

Naabhi kati udar anup re, tiyaan trivali shobe sukhroop re;
Jamane ure shrivats chihn re, neerkhi harake jan pavan re.

Here is the translation:

Say Srikrishna Purushottam Ra, Vasudeva Vishnu Parambrahm Ra;
Hari Narayan Antaryami Ra, Bhagavan Prabhu Bahunami Ra. 63

Victory to Laxmi, the beautiful one, in Shashikalā; 
Mādhavī Jamunā, she is auspicious there;
Rati Kānti, her face is like Chandramukhi; 
Kadambamālikā, herself possessing great power, is happy.

Here is the translation:

Parijata Krishna priya Nandu ra, Nam Nandinisundari sukhada ra;
Eh Adi sundari apara ra, Seve Shrikrishnane kari pyar ra; 69

Here is the translation:

He who has not been blessed, does not come near; whoever worships Lord here in devotion; 
Hari Dhari himself takes avatar, this Dhama's boundary will be crossed at twelve.
